    <section id="id42394056">
      <title>Memorandum</title>
      <para id="id42394066">Water:</para>
      <list id="id42228235" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>H<sub>2</sub>O</item>
        <item>Hydrogen and oxygen</item>
        <item>The elements oxygen and hydrogen joined. This formed a new substance, namely water, that consists of two types of atoms. The atoms joined to form a water molecule.</item>
        <item>Yes, the elements are combined in a fixed relation to form a new substance with new characteristics.</item>
      </list>
      <figure id="id46679606">
        <media id="id46679606_media" alt="">
          <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics1-942c.png" id="id46679606__onlineimage" height="145" width="365"/>
